high_descs: Turn around and walk to the right hand sink.
Pick up the bottle of soap on the edge of the counter.
Move to your left so you face the counter to the left of the left sink.
Put the soap on the back of the toilet.
Turn around and walk to the wall then turn left and walk to the tub.
Pick up the soap that's on the edge of the tub.
Walk back to where you put the first bottle of soap.
Put this bottle of soap by the first one you put on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put two bottles of liquid soap on the toilet.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink on the vanity.
Pick up the silver bottle of soap to the right of the sink on the vanity.
Turn around and walk to the white toilet on the right.
Put the bottle of soap on the left side of the toilet tank.
Turn around and walk to the tub on the left.
Pick up the silver bottle of soap on the edge of the tub.
Turn around and walk to the white toilet on the right.
Put the silver bottle of soap behind the other silver bottle of soap on the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Place two bottles of soap on a toilet tank.

high_descs: Turn right take on step then turn right and go towards the counter.
Pick up the hand soap bottle from the counter.
Turn around take one step then turn right go to the end of the counter and then turn right at the corner of the counter.
Put the soap bottle on top of the toilet tank beside the green spray bottle.
Turn around walk to the end of the bathroom then turn left and walk towards the bath tub.
Pick up the hand soap bottle from the bath tub.
Turn around walk towards the door then turn right and go to the counter.
Put the Soap bottle on toilet tank behind the existing bottles.
anns.task_desc: Move the Soap bottles to the Toilet Tank.
